
It's easy to make the case for why User Account Control is a good idea but it's a bit more challenging to make it work in the real world.   

In this webinar I will acquaint you with how UAC works and how you can make it part of of an overall way to once and for all allow users to run without administrator authority and avoid all the assocated risks. However there are some important caveats with using UAC in the real world. 


